<i>and whose body was allegedly--</i>

36:21.596 --> 36:24.390
<i>Was I wrong?</i>
<i>Did I come on too strong?</i>

36:25.057 --> 36:27.143
<i>Or will you take the bait</i>
<i>and suggest we meet?</i>

36:31.189 --> 36:34.275
<i>Great. I'm in purgatory. You won't talk</i>
<i>to</i> <i>me, Kate won't talk to</i> <i>me.</i>

36:34.358 --> 36:37.570
<i>So I'm still watching her window.</i>
<i>This is perfect. Thank you.</i>

37:06.098 --> 37:08.601
<i>I guess I'm not the only one in purgatory.</i>

37:19.320 --> 37:23.282
<i>If she can't shed a tear, at least</i>
<i>she can destroy that heinous portrait.</i>

37:48.224 --> 37:49.558
<i>I hope it helps.</i>

37:51.769 --> 37:52.937
<i>Shit.</i>

38:11.247 --> 38:14.875
<i>-There you are-- Shit, it's just Phoebe.</i>

38:25.052 --> 38:27.513
Oh. Come on in. Just give me a second.

38:27.596 --> 38:30.224
<i>With all this mystery</i>
<i>and ambiguity you stuck me in,</i>

38:30.308 --> 38:34.020
<i>I can at least do one simple good thing</i>
<i>for a good person.</i>

38:34.103 --> 38:37.231
-My God, thank you.
-Don't worry. I didn't read it.

38:37.315 --> 38:40.901
Well, I wouldn't care if you had.
It's very well-written.

38:43.446 --> 38:47.366
I was reminded of this recently.
I think it might help you.

38:47.450 --> 38:48.326
Joan Didion.

38:52.455 --> 38:53.998
I can't believe he's dead.

38:56.083 --> 38:58.669
I've never known anyone
that's died before.

39:00.963 --> 39:03.174
-It feels awful.
-Yeah, it does.

39:05.176 --> 39:06.177
Until it doesn't.

39:09.388 --> 39:10.473
When will that be?

39:10.973 --> 39:13.642
I think that looks different on everybody.

39:14.810 --> 39:17.146
The guilt only makes it worse.

39:17.229 --> 39:19.523
I don't think you should feel guilty
for loving anybody.

39:20.232 --> 39:21.525
I didn't love him.

39:22.485 --> 39:23.986
Okay, caring, then.

39:24.570 --> 39:29.492
Sometimes we care for the wrong people
and it doesn't make us bad, only human.

39:33.746 --> 39:34.580
Thank you.

39:37.541 --> 39:39.543
I'll see you in class.

39:39.627 --> 39:40.669
Okay.

39:48.427 --> 39:52.348
<i>I need to follow my own advice.</i>
<i>Stop feeling so guilty.</i>

39:53.349 --> 39:56.310
<i>I've made mistakes, but I can do better.</i>

40:01.107 --> 40:03.776
<i>"I think it's time for us to meet."</i>
<i>It</i> <i>worked.</i>

40:03.859 --> 40:06.278
<i>And now I understand how to talk to you.</i>

40:07.279 --> 40:08.906
<i>"One condition.</i>

40:08.989 --> 40:11.158
<i>Leave Kate alone. She's mine."</i>

40:13.244 --> 40:15.329
<i>"There's the Joe I've been looking for."</i>

40:15.413 --> 40:18.874
<i>Now that Kate's off-limits and I don't</i>
<i>need to run around bodyguarding her...</i>

40:18.958 --> 40:20.960
<i>"When and where?"</i>

40:23.421 --> 40:24.505
<i>"Details soon."</i>

40:30.302 --> 40:31.804
<i>How soon?</i>

40:33.431 --> 40:35.933
<i>No more texting, no more games.</i>

40:41.439 --> 40:43.232
<i>This can't be good.</i>

40:51.031 --> 40:54.702
Professor Moore. If we might have
the briefest moment of your time?

40:56.078 --> 40:58.247
Or course. Anything to help.
